              <p>
                <span
                  >G\xF6r\xFCld\xFC\u011F\xFC \xFCzere \xE7ift yarat\u0131lma \xF6zelli\u011Fi hem bitkiler hem canl\u0131lar
                  hem insanlar hem de Allah\u2019\u0131n d\u0131\u015F\u0131nda bilmedi\u011Fimiz b\xFCt\xFCn varl\u0131klar
                  i\xE7in ge\xE7erlidir. Mesela elektrikte art\u0131 ve eksi kutuplar, cisimler
                  aras\u0131nda itme ve \xE7ekme kuvveti, atomlardaki pozitif ve negatif
                  elektronlar bile bu \xE2yetin m\xFBcizev\xEE olarak haber verdi\u011Fi \u015Feyler
                  aras\u0131nda say\u0131l\u0131r. \xC2yetin a\xE7t\u0131\u011F\u0131 ufkun ayd\u0131nl\u0131\u011F\u0131nda yap\u0131lacak ilm\xEE
                  \xE7al\u0131\u015Fmalar, bu alanda daha nice dikkat \xE7ekici ince sonu\xE7lar\u0131n
                  ortaya \xE7\u0131kmas\u0131n\u0131 sa\u011Flayacakt\u0131r. B\xFCt\xFCn bunlardan maksat ise, her
                  \u015Feyi \xE7ift yaratan Allah\u2019\u0131n tek oldu\u011Funu; O\u2019nun e\u015Fi ve orta\u011F\u0131
                  bulunmad\u0131\u011F\u0131n\u0131 bey\xE2nd\u0131r.</span
                >
              </p>

